Package game.actions

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    SimpleFunction
    an interface that defines a simple function with no arguments and no return
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    AdvancedMoveAction
    this class is an action class that works in a similar way to MovaActorAction but it has the added functionality of sending a signal
    AttackAction
    Abstract class that is inherited by different attacks
    BreakShellAction
    A class for breaking shells, extends Action class
    BuyAction
    Class for buying items from toad, extends action class
    ConsumeAction
    A class representing ConsumeAction, extends Action class
    ConsumeWaterAction
    Class for Actors to consume water from fountain that extends action
    DefaultAttackAction
    A default attack action that has no extra effects to the target, extends AttackAction
    DrinkAction
    Class for drinking water from the bottle
    EndGameAction
    Special action to end the game
    FireAttackAction
    A attack action that not only hurts the target, but also drops a fire at target's ground.
    InteractAction
    Class for getting bottle from taod
    JumpAction
    an action a player can use to move to a HighGround block
    RefillAction
    Class for refilling water into bottle
    ResetGameAction
    an action that is used by the player to reset the game
    SuicideAction
    Special action for Goomba to suicide
